---
---

<section class="quality-pledge-section" id="quality">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        我们的承诺
      </span>
      <h2 class="section-title">透明、开放、可信赖</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        我们深信，开源项目的长久发展建立在透明和信任之上
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pledge-grid">
      <div class="pledge-card">
        <div class="card-accent" style="--accent-color: #3b82f6;"></div>
        <div class="pledge-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="pledge-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pledge-title">完全开源</h3>
        <p class="pledge-description">
          代码完整托管于 GitHub，接受社区审查。不隐藏任何核心逻辑，您可以深入了解每一行代码的实现细节。
        </p>
        <div class="pledge-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/smartboot/smart-servlet" target="_blank" class="pledge-link">
            <span>浏览代码</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pledge-card">
        <div class="card-accent" style="--accent-color: #22c55e;"></div>
        <div class="pledge-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="pledge-icon" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e, #16a34a);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pledge-title">文档完善</h3>
        <p class="pledge-description">
          提供详尽的安装指南、API 文档和最佳实践。从入门到精通，每个阶段都有清晰的技术文档支持。
        </p>
        <div class="pledge-links">
          <a href="./guides/about/" class="pledge-link">
            <span>查看文档</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pledge-card">
        <div class="card-accent" style="--accent-color: #f59e0b;"></div>
        <div class="pledge-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="pledge-icon" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" x2="8" y1="13" y2="13"/><line x1="16" x2="8" y1="17" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pledge-title">测试透明</h3>
        <p class="pledge-description">
          性能测试方法、TCK 测试报告全部公开。您可以复现所有测试结果，确保数据的真实性和可信度。
        </p>
        <div class="pledge-links">
          <a href="./guides/tck_report/" class="pledge-link">
            <span>TCK 报告</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pledge-card">
        <div class="card-accent" style="--accent-color: #ec4899;"></div>
        <div class="pledge-icon-wrapper">
          <div class="pledge-icon" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ec4899, #db2777);">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pledge-title">社区支持</h3>
        <p class="pledge-description">
          活跃的开发者社区，Gitee Issues 及时响应。您的问题和建议都会被认真对待，共同推进项目发展。
        </p>
        <div class="pledge-links">
          <a href="https://gitee.com/smartboot/smart-servlet/issues" target="_blank" class="pledge-link">
            <span>问题反馈</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .quality-pledge-section {
    padding: var(--space-24) var(--space-4);
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    position: relative;
  }

  .quality-pledge-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 800px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-color), transparent);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #f59e0b;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .badge-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #f59e0b;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; transform: scale(1.1); }
  }

  :root[data-theme="light"] .section-badge {
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.06);
    border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .pledge-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .pledge-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pledge-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .pledge-card {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    transition: all var(--transition-slow);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card-accent {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .pledge-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .pledge-card:hover .card-accent {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .pledge-icon-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .pledge-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-primary), var(--accent-secondary));
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
  }

  .pledge-title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
  }

  .pledge-description {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .pledge-links {
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .pledge-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3);
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .pledge-link:hover {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .pledge-link svg {
    transition: transform var(--transition-base);
  }

  .pledge-link:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(2px);
  }
</style>
